             GUNNELL. I am a Police-constable. I took Wadmore in Pye-street two days after this.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310512-184-person1380">
                  HENRY 
                  PIPER
               <interp inst="t18310512-184-person1380" type="surname" value="PIPER"></interp>
